{%- comment -%}
  BKS Studio Archive — exclusive content for bks-archive tier
  Rendered inside bks-member-dashboard tab OR standalone via page.bks-archive.json
  Access guard is handled by the caller (tier check before render).
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="bks-archive-header">
  <p class="bks-archive-eyebrow">BKS Studio Archive</p>
  <h2 class="bks-archive-title">Il processo. Non il prodotto.</h2>
  <p class="bks-archive-sub">
    Quello che pubblichiamo è il 10% di quello che creiamo. Qui c'è il resto —
    prompt reali, pattern scartati, note di processo. Uso personale.
  </p>
</div>

{%- comment -%} ── Prompt Library ── {%- endcomment -%}
<div style="margin-bottom:40px;">
  <p class="bks-section-title">Prompt Library — parziale</p>
  <div class="bks-archive-grid">

    <div class="bks-archive-card">
      <div class="bks-archive-card-thumb">🧬</div>
      <div class="bks-archive-card-body">
        <p class="bks-archive-card-cat">Prompt · Glyph Collection</p>
        <h3 class="bks-archive-card-title">Pattern generativi — strutture molecolari</h3>
        <p class="bks-archive-card-desc">
          I prompt base usati per generare la famiglia di pattern Glyph — simmetria, densità, varianti cromatiche.
        </p>
        <p class="bks-archive-card-meta">8 prompt · Midjourney v6 + Stable Diffusion</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bks-archive-card">
      <div class="bks-archive-card-thumb">🎨</div>
      <div class="bks-archive-card-body">
        <p class="bks-archive-card-cat">Prompt · Folklore Collection</p>
        <h3 class="bks-archive-card-title">Tessuti etnici rielaborati — layer AI</h3>
        <p class="bks-archive-card-desc">
          Come abbiamo tradotto riferimenti tessili tradizionali in pattern print-ready con AI.
        </p>
        <p class="bks-archive-card-meta">12 prompt · Adobe Firefly + Midjourney</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bks-archive-card">
      <div class="bks-archive-card-thumb">⚡</div>
      <div class="bks-archive-card-body">
        <p class="bks-archive-card-cat">Prompt · Pulse Collection</p>
        <h3 class="bks-archive-card-title">Energy patterns — gradient e movimento</h3>
        <p class="bks-archive-card-desc">
          Prompt per pattern che evocano energia cinetica. Iterazioni e prompt negativi inclusi.
        </p>
        <p class="bks-archive-card-meta">6 prompt · Stable Diffusion XL</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bks-archive-card" style="border-style:dashed;opacity:0.5;">
      <div class="bks-archive-card-thumb">🔒</div>
      <div class="bks-archive-card-body">
        <p class="bks-archive-card-cat">Prompt · Marker Collection</p>
        <h3 class="bks-archive-card-title">Calligrafia e segno grafico</h3>
        <p class="bks-archive-card-desc">In arrivo — prossimo aggiornamento archivio.</p>
        <p class="bks-archive-card-meta">Presto disponibile</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

